      "author": "zinverno",
      "description": "## What's new\r\n\r\n- **Live free models list for OpenRouter** — new button in settings fetches the current list of free models (with context sizes) directly from OpenRouter, so you never end up with a removed model\r\n- Command names no longer duplicate the plugin name\r\n\r\n## Code quality (community catalog review)\r\n\r\n- `window.setTimeout` / `window.clearTimeout` for popout window compatibility\r\n- Respect custom config directory (`Vault#configDir`) instead of hardcoded `.obsidian`\r\n- Typed OpenRouter API responses and editor internals — removed remaining `any` casts\r\n- Async event handlers properly wrapped (no floating promises)\r\n- CSS: dropped `!important` overrides in favor of specific selectors, fixed scrollbar lint warnings",
